1012.name: AA 66B
1012.Applications: Rebuilding wornout parts or protecting new machine parts to increase life that suffer from extreme abrasive wear
1012.Suitable_For: 64-68 HRc Hardfacing wire used in mining, agriculture and steel mills, conveyor chains, agriculture, construction, mixer blades, paddles, cement pumps with excelent abrasion and wear resistance against sand and minerals
